        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In all such cases Apis is of the best use to us; it is even sufficient to arrest the disorganizing process, and to bring about a satisfactorily progressing cure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "The curative indications contained in the \"American Provings,\" have been confirmed by my own experience.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "From all this we deduce the highly important practical rule: In a case of whitlow, first ascertain whether and how far Sulphur has been abused by the patient.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Unfortunately the non abuse of Sulphur is an exception to the rule, whereas the abuse of Sulphur is quite common even in our age.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Would that in this respect the ancient darkness might yield to the new light.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In case Sulphur had been abused by the patient, we mix a few drops of Apis three in twelve tablespoonfuls of water, giving a tablespoonful every hour, or every two or three hours, according as the pains are more or less violent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In either case the medicine need not be repeated, and the organic reaction will be sufficient to complete a cure without the interference of surgery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "A simple bread and milk poultice may be used as soothing palliative, especially if the external skin is of a firm, hard texture. Resolution may be depended upon in every case, where Apis has been resorted to in time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "If the Sulphur miasm gains the ascendancy, there will be no marked improvement during the first days of the treatment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In such a case we have at once to resort to a very high potency of Sulphur.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000017_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000017_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "A single globule of Sulphur six thousand would frequently ameliorate the worst aspect of the case as by a miracle, after which a few more doses of Apis three, a drop morning and evening, would so improve the symptoms, as to render all further medication unnecessary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98878_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98878/7398_98878_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "These explanations likewise point out the true course to be pursued, in case we should at the outset find that a whitlow owes its existence to the psoric miasm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "DYSENTERY.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Who has not often felt embarrassed to select the right remedy among three or four that seemed indicated by the symptoms, and where it was nevertheless important, in view of the threatening danger, to select at once the right remedy?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Who has not been struck by the strange irregularity that in a disease which generally sets in as an epidemic, different remedies are often indicated by different groups of symptoms?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "This truth is abundantly confirmed by experience.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "All my previously obtained results in practice, testify to the correctness of this statement.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "At the very commencement of the disease, a globule of Apis three is sufficient to cut short the disease so that the patient feels easy, and sleeps quietly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Under these circumstances we repeat the medicine every hour, or every two or three hours, one globule at a time, until all further medication has become unnecessary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "As far as my personal observations go, I am disposed to affirm that the best mode of effecting a good result, is to give Apis three and Aconite three, in alternation, one drop of each preparation well shaken in a bottle containing twelve tablespoonfuls of water, and giving a tablespoonful every hour or three hours, if the danger is great, and in milder cases a full drop alternately morning and evening.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "This end is not always attained with equal certainty and rapidity, if Apis is not given in alternation with Aconite.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In such a case, Apis alone often develops a powerful reaction, which is avoided by the alternate use of Aconite.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In most cases I have seen a few alternate doses give rise to a pleasant perspiration, speedily followed by quiet sleep and recovery on waking.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "May we not expect the same result at the commencement of Asiatic cholera, and thus arrest the further development of the disease?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Scarcely has the little being seen the light of the world, when the process of purgation begins.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "It is his habit, in after life, to combat every little costiveness, every digestive derangement, every incipient disease, by means of his cathartic mixture, and his skill is considered proportionate to the quantity of stuff which the bowels expel under the operation of his drugs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Laxative pills, rhubarb, glauber salts, bitter waters, aloes, gin, etc, etc, are in every body's hands, and become an increasing necessity for millions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Those who cannot afford to go to the springs, use artificial mineral water in order to accomplish similar purposes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000011_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000011_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "It is still a profitable business to sell patent purgatives, such as cider in which a little magnesia has been dissolved.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "In spite of all this, long habit has secured to these pernicious customs a sort of prescriptive right.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "The distress consequent upon them, increases in proportion as the reactive powers of the organism decrease, which is more particularly the case in the present generation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Indeed, the old proverb is again verified: \"Where need is greatest, there help is nearest.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "The world is not only indebted to Hahnemann for a knowledge, but also for a natural corrective of this serious abuse.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "Few men, if their attention has once been directed to this abuse, will feel disposed to deny its extent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7398_98880_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7398/98880/7398_98880_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7398",
        "content": "It should be considered a duty by every physician, to be acquainted with the new means of cure. The continued use of purgatives should be considered a crime against health.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
